column4: "Played in real time - not edited - using Steinberg's 'The Grand'. The idea for this treatment came from Kenny Werner's performance on his Maybeck Hall solo piano CD\012"
"Very simple LH repetitive figure - 'Music Box'-style high in the treble register"
"Contrasts with 'lusher' more complex harmonies through the bridge played rubato"
"Improvised solo section - simple folk-like lines over the A section"
"Again the bridge played with more complex chords/harmonies out of tempo"
